Class AbstractSettingsModelRangeBounded<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.SettingsModel
      • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.AbstractSettingsModelRangeBounded<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the value to store
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SettingsModelComparableRangeBounded<T>, SettingsModelRangeBounded<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SettingsModelDateRangeBounded, SettingsModelDoubleRangeBounded, SettingsModelIntegerRangeBounded

    public abstract class AbstractSettingsModelRangeBounded<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.SettingsModel
implements SettingsModelComparableRangeBounded<T>
    An abstract base implementaion class SettingsModel for the SettingsModelComparableRangeBounded interface. Implementing classes must implement the readValue(NodeSettingsRO, String) and writeValue(NodeSettingsWO, String, Comparable) methods
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
